<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Distinct2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Distinct,</orth> adj. 1) <emph>distínct,</emph> marked out, specified: <cit><quote>and make d. the very breach,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 4.5.245" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 5, 245</bibl></cit>. 2) <emph>dístinct,</emph> different, separate: <bibl n="shak. mv 2.9.61" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 9, 61</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 4.4.47" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 4, 47</bibl>. But cf. <bibl default="NO">Appendix I, 1</bibl>.
